to build vmime in fedora use:
    * sudo dnf install libgsasl.x86_64
    * sudo dnf install libgsasl-devel.x86_64
    * sudo dnf install sendmail.x86_64
    * sudo dnf install libuuid.x86_64
    * sudo dnf install libuuid-devel.x86_64
    * sudo dnf install gnutls-devel.x86_64
    * cd /path/to/vmime-build
    * cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" /path/to/vmime-source (may you need to excute in src directory)
    * cmake --build .
    * sudo make install